        <h1 class="mb20"><span class="lightText">Help: </span>Directory Submission Guidelines</h1>

        <hr />
        All items submitted to the Directory must meet our guidelines. We have these guidelines in place so that we can ensure 
	    only relevant content is submitted, and content which is legally able to be published. Please ensure that when submitting an 
	    item, that it meets the following criteria. Failure to meet these guidelines will result in your item not being 
	    published.

        <ul class="mt20 mb20">
            <li>All items must be related to motorcycling</li>
            <li>All items must be UK relevant</li>
            <li>Images musn't exceed 500 pixels in width, and 500 in height</li>
            <li>Links must take the user to the organisation, or company in question</li>
            <li>No profane, racist, libelous or deflamatory content can be submitted</li>
            <li>Only genuine items should be submitted</li>
        </ul>

        <i class="lightText">Please note, that we reserve the right to determine what will and will not be published.</i>

